774 \ubc24; ''I bam'')}}\n| Released as part of the 2019 BTS anniversary event Festa\n| <ref name=\"Tonight\" />\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Writing credits ===\nAll song credits are adapted from the [[Korea Music Copyright Association]]'s database, unless otherwise noted.<ref name=\"KMCA\">{{cite web|title=Songs Registered Under Jin (10005243)|url=http://www.komca.or.kr/foreign2/eng/S01.jsp|website=komca.or.kr|accessdate=2018-01-19}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:10em;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:10em;\"|Artist\n! style=\"width:17em;\"|Album\n! style=\"width:20em;\"|Song\n|-\n| 2013\n| rowspan=5|[[BTS]]\n|  ''[[2 Cool 4 Skool]]''\n| \"Outro: Circle Room Cypher\" \n|-\n| rowspan=2|2015\n| rowspan=2|''[[The Most Beautiful Moment in Life, Part 1]]''\t\n| \"Outro: Love Is Not Over\"\t\n|-\t\t\n| \"Boyz with Fun\"\t\n|-\n| rowspan=2|2016\n|  ''[[The Most Beautiful Moment in Life: Young Forever]]''\t\n| \"Love Is Not Over\"\n|-\n| ''[[Wings (BTS album)|Wings]]''\n| \"Awake\" \n|-\n| 2019\n| Jin\n| {{N/A|Non-album release}}\n| \"Tonight\"<ref name=\"Tonight\" />\n|- \n| 2020\n| [[BTS]]\n| ''[[Map of the Soul: 7]]''\n| \"Moon\"\n|}\n\n== Filmography ==\n[[File:Kim Seok-jin at a fanmeet in Ilsan, in March 2014 04.jpg|alt=Kim faces forward, pursing his lips|thumb|upright|Kim at a fanmeet in [[Ilsan-gu]] on March 1, 2014.]]\n{{See also|BTS videography}}\n\n=== Trailers and short films ===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"  \n|+\n! Year\n! Title   \n! Length   \n! Director(s)          \n! '''Ref.'''\n|-\n| rowspan=1|2016\n| \"Awake #7\"     \n| 5:19\n| rowspan=2|Yong-seok Choi (Lumpens)\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=\u9632\u5f3e\u5c11\u5e74\u56e3\u3001\u6700\u5f8c\u306e\u30b7\u30e7\u30fc\u30c8\u30d5\u30a3\u30eb\u30e0\u306e\u4e3b\u4eba\u516c\u306f\u30b8\u30f3\u2026\u30ab\u30e0\u30d0\u30c3\u30af\u3078\u306e\"\u30ab\u30a6\u30f3\u30c8\u30c0\u30a6\u30f3\" |url=http://news.kstyle.com/article.ksn?articleNo=2052585 |website=kstyle |accessdate=17 October 2018 |language=Japanese